   "t": 24524,
   "s": "err",
   "x": "## Spec"
  },
  {
   "t": 24524,
   "s": "err",
   "x": "- Input: a CSV string. Output: array of rows, each row an array of string fields."
  },
  {
   "t": 24524,
   "s": "err",
   "x": "- Fields are separated by commas. Rows by `\\n` or `\\r\\n`."
  },
  {
   "t": 24524,
   "s": "err",
   "x": "- A field may be quoted with double quotes. Inside a quoted field: commas and newlines are literal, and `\"\"` is an escaped literal quote."
  },
  {
   "t": 24524,
   "s": "err",
   "x": "- Empty fields are empty strings. A trailing newline at the end of input does NOT produce an extra empty row."
  },
  {
   "t": 24524,
   "s": "err",
   "x": "## Examples"
  },
  {
   "t": 24524,
   "s": "err",
   "x": "```js"
  },
  {
   "t": 24524,
   "s": "err",
   "x": "parseCSV('a,b,c')            // [['a','b','c']]"
  },
  {
   "t": 24524,
